title: Gustave Caillebotte Paris Street; Rainy Day Eyeglass Case with Cloth
description:
Eyeglass Case developed from Gustave Caillebotte Paris Street; Rainy Day, 1877, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Keep it close, carry it with you, our hard shell eyeglass case is the perfect accessory. Matching microfiber lens cloth included. 

  • Dimensions: Glass Case: 6.25 x 2.25 x 1.25 in. Cloth: 6 x7 in.
  • Materials: Plastic, microfiber.
